        <h5 class="section-text" style="text-align: justify; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 20px">3 Palms Intelligent Video Solutions, LLC was founded to provide cloud storage services for small and medium sized businesses by securing surveillance video and corresponding Point of Sale (POS) data off site. Adding redundancy to, or replacing, your on-site recording hardware with a cloud storage platform will significantly reduce the risk of a catastrophic video/detail loss. This can truly make a difference to your bottom line and your employee/customers wellbeing.</h5>
        <p class="section-text" style="text-align: justify; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 20px">Utilizing a cloud managed VSaaS (Video Solutions as a Service) approach, you have the option to supplement or replace local evidentiary video storage hardware with that of a secure off-site storage solution. This method eliminates the need for you to purchase costly capital expense hardware and subsequent Maintenance Agreements, while providing an annual fixed subscription budget and optimizing the management of your existing video investment.</p>
        <h6 class="section-text" style="text-align: justify; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px">Camera Video to Cloud Storage</h6>
        <p class="section-text">Provide a direct and secure off-site connection to manage, retrieve and review Loss Prevention and Operational video/data without requiring traditional DVR/NVR hardware.</p>
        <h6 class="section-text" style="text-align: justify; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px">Camera Video Storage to Cloud Storage</h6>
        <p class="section-text">Eliminate the need for local servers, firewall equipment and NVRs with an on-board solid state video storage camera solution that provides 24/7 access to live video feeds.</p>
        <h6 class="section-text" style="text-align: justify; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px">Point of Sale (POS) Video/Exception Reporting to Cloud Storage</h6>
        <p class="section-text">Automate the management, storage, and retrieval of POS Video/Transactional activity with a scalable cloud-based and secured platform.</p>
        <p class="section-text">In addition, our select Video Manufacturer partnerships provide 3 Palms the ability to provide cost-effective options to supplement/upgrade your existing Video investments.</p>
        <hr class="section-text"/>
        <p class="section-text" style="text-align: right; font-style: italic;">"Never doubt that a small group of people can change the world; indeed, it is the only thing that ever has."</p>
        <p class="section-text" style="text-align: right;">- Margaret Mead </p>
    </div>
